\begin_layout Standard
There are therefore an infinity of Nash equilibria of the entry game, of
 which one PSNE, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \text{Enter, }p_{I}=0\right\} $
\end_inset

 and an infinite range of mixed strategy Nash equilibria denoted 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \text{Stay out,}p_{I}\geq\frac{1}{2}\right\} .$
\end_inset

 Note that the PSNE 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \text{Stay out, }p_{I}=1\right\} $
\end_inset

