\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
Consider the following `tit-for-tat' conditional stage game strategy: Play
 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 in the first period.
 In the 
\begin_inset Formula $t^{th}$
\end_inset

 period, and if the other player played 
